ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAddition to Whitefish River Indian Reserve No. 4, Ontario
PrecisOrder setting apart 749.85 hectares (1,852.85 acres) of land for the use and benefit of the Whitefish River First Nation as an addition to WHITEFISH RIVER INDIAN RESERVE NO. 4, located in the geographic Geographic Township of Curtin, approximately 25 kilometres from the Town of Espanola, Ontario.
